            <h2>Istoric</h2>
            <p>Pack & Go a luat nastere in <time datetime="2016">2016</time> in urma unei calatorii prin Europa.</p>
            <aside id="aside1">
                <figure>
                    <img id="img1" src="/png/calatorie.png" alt="Importanta rucsacurilor" title="Calatorie prin europa">
